To Run the chatbot follow these steps :
1. Install Tensorflow, Keras , Pickle-mixin through anaconda navigator or anaconda prompt.
2.  (a) Now open a Jupyter notebook file and type the following:
         import nltk
         nltk.download('punkt')
         nltk.download()
    (b) Now a window will open. Go to "All Packages" and click on download. close the window once donloads complete.
    (c)now in the next line type :
         import tensorflow as tf
         tf.compat.v1.global_variables(scope=None)
         
3. Open anaconda prompt, set the directory to the path where the files are stored.
4. Run the following commands:
   python train_chatbot.py
   python chatgui.py
     
